{"tid":1386759,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請300萬人出嚟逼獨立調查，由個委員會判斷檢控定特赦","createTime":"2019-07-30T11:49:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T14:43:44.000Z","uid":266060,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9eadedfc584ff6a1b13e75cb758777b877617810","tid":1386759,"uid":266060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:49:54.000Z","msg":"而家講乜都係假<br />\n我地要300萬人出嚟爭取獨立調查委員會<br />\n講明<span style=\"color: red;\">要由個委員會判斷應唔應該檢控、點樣檢控犯法嘅人（包括示威者同警察）</span><br />\n定係放過晒兩班人，社會大和解<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">凡有人性嘅，都應該企出嚟支持</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n理由：<br />\n1. 示威者係表達政治訴求<br />\n2. 警隊係呢次爭議嘅其中一方，有根本性嘅利益衝突，社會唔會信任佢地嘅決定。Justice must be seen to be done!"},{"pid":"daa263d423a8edfcc2fd3234d367b0b0c2334beb","tid":1386759,"uid":266060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:50:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54aac3ff7421566aad75b622fa89349dd9e4a023","tid":1386759,"uid":266060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:50:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc7000ff724a47eead7d48af873cec7071affe9d","tid":1386759,"uid":266060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:51:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbe763a5874c70450cf1b3e3c93b40cb703f26a9","tid":1386759,"uid":142803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:52:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f1416bc010f318ba0a64086af696d13c0b6b5475","tid":1386759,"uid":266060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:52:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>It's now persecution, not prosecution!</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"7353046d416834dd1777fa9240952e4b8cb0b6c7","tid":1386759,"uid":266060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:54:24.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">It's persecution, not prosecution!</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"7ea26dce017b5bad9e4047575e6362aae399687a","tid":1386759,"uid":292888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:58:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6672138ebaec6a55d5fc0c43fd1f192be17182c9","tid":1386759,"uid":292888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:06:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e42b533c328c65761d540bc0cc1e9e91d0835cd8","tid":1386759,"uid":266798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:09:24.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d45308607497e6f8b6dd04bc3a866f53706c4a38","tid":1386759,"uid":50341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:11:23.000Z","msg":"係要自行成立啊屌<br />\n佢搵班紅底既成立有撚用咩"},{"pid":"0e5bae4d72b021d6cb9a918bd12b401bfd29ff4c","tid":1386759,"uid":232065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:14:05.000Z","msg":"你認為會特赦既，唔知話你天真定on9<br />\n會特赦既根本唔會告呢條罪<br />\n了解一下共產黨既手法，佢地永遠都係要散播白色恐怖"},{"pid":"44d8eeb41471c1cdb4dd449d7fe92b947f891d57","tid":1386759,"uid":266060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:35:00.000Z","msg":"希望大家明白，而家個問題喺邊<br />\n<br />\nA同B打交，由C嚟介入、起訴，相對持平<br />\n但如果A同B打交，由A嚟起訴，咁就叫<span style=\"color: red;\">利益衝突</span><br />\n<br />\n雖然示威者係不滿政府，要撤回、雙普選等<br />\n但其中一個訴求係徹查黑警<br />\n而大家都有眼見到，黑警係激發人街頭抗爭嘅重要原因<br />\n<br />\n呢種情況下，由警察去搜證、建議起訴，本身就有<span style=\"color: red;\">利益衝突</span><br />\n你睇下佢地有心放生白衣人、放生同袍<br />\n但又用最重嘅暴動罪想釘死44個義士就知<br />\n真係有利益衝突<br />\n<br />\n所以我地一定要成立另一個獨立機構<br />\n話之佢叫獨立調查委員會又好，真相委員會又好<br />\n由佢去持平地建議律政司，係咪仲告落去<br />\n或者建議特首，罪成後係咪應該特赦晒所有人<br />\n<br />\n呢個係200萬甚至更多人都應該會支持嘅方案<br />\n我地而家要嘅係動員晒大家出嚟，支持suspend既定機制<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好畀警察去負責處理呢壇野</span>"},{"pid":"5e6f1409e7d2740c98b17d86130eeb08f44fefbd","tid":1386759,"uid":266060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:35:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ffea49b7fe58bb895ce6aa213f40fc79e31960b","tid":1386759,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:36:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"199fb0e3457133bfc666cf7ab12a5c897027af03","tid":1386759,"uid":266060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:42:40.000Z","msg":"【推出去】營救義士，成立「真相與和解委員會」<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dthkRS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dthkRS</a>"},{"pid":"284a89104fcb1bf4804589fdeb08eb8d6723e8f6","tid":1386759,"uid":65790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:43:44.000Z","msg":"正確"}]}